Bug 204612 - Add "Copy To" folder context menu for message/rfc822 attachments. r=mkmelin

Allow copying attached messages (message/rfc822) directly to a mail folder
via the attachment item context menu. The menu is only shown when all
selected attachments are of type message/rfc822 (or have an .eml filename
as fallback for messages with wrong MIME type), and uses the existing
folder-menupopup for folder selection and AttachmentInfo.importToFolder()
for the import.

Also wrap the importToFolder temp-file lifecycle in try/finally to ensure
cleanup even when copyFileMessageAsync fails.

Differential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D308590


